These features are the current goals of the catfacts. This may change.

+ [ catfacts Features ]
  - Command Line Interface

+ [ catfacts-client Features ]
  - Commmand Line Interface
  - Interactive CLI Interface
  - Client
  - Manage/View Data

+ [ catfacts-server Features ]
  - Address book stored in DBMS
  - Alarms stored in DBMS
  - Alarms (fact to execute send to # at specific time)
